label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"鸡蛔虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":20,"end":23,"text":"蛔虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":24,"end":30,"text":"影响生长发育","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":31,"end":38,"text":"严重的引起死亡","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 鸡蛔虫病，在大群饲养情况下，雏鸡常由于患蛔虫病而影响生长发育，严重的引起死亡。

label: [{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"死鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"线虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"小肠","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":24,"end":28,"text":"堵塞肠道","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 当剖解死鸡时，小肠内常发现大小如细豆芽样的线虫，堵塞肠道。虫体少则几条，多则数百条。

label: [{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"肠粘膜发炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"发炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":22,"text":"黄白色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"肠粘膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":52,"end":54,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 肠粘膜发炎、水肿、充血。成年蛔虫虫体呈黄白色，雄虫长50～76毫米，雌虫长60～116毫米。3月龄以下的雏鸡最易感染。
蛔虫可以在鸡体内交配、产卵，虫卵可以在鸡体内生长也可以随粪便被排出体外，地面上的虫卵被鸡啄食后进入体内造成鸡群感染。从吞食虫卵到发育成虫，大约需要35～58天。

label: [{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"幼鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":12,"end":16,"text":"食欲减退","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":17,"end":21,"text":"生长迟缓","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"呆立少动","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":27,"end":31,"text":"消瘦虚弱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":32,"end":36,"text":"粘膜苍白","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":34,"end":36,"text":"苍白","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":37,"end":41,"text":"羽毛松乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":39,"end":41,"text":"松乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":42,"end":46,"text":"两翅下垂","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":44,"end":46,"text":"下垂","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":47,"end":51,"text":"胸骨突出","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":49,"end":51,"text":"突出","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":52,"end":59,"text":"下痢和便秘交替","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":62,"end":71,"text":"粪便中有带血的粘液","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":74,"end":81,"text":"逐渐消瘦而死亡","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"粘膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"羽毛","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":42,"end":44,"text":"两翅","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":47,"end":49,"text":"胸骨","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":62,"end":64,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 临床症状：幼鸡患病表现为食欲减退，生长迟缓，呆立少动，消瘦虚弱，粘膜苍白、羽毛松乱，两翅下垂，胸骨突出，下痢和便秘交替，有时粪便中有带血的粘液，以后逐渐消瘦而死亡。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"下痢","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"日渐消瘦","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":27,"end":31,"text":"产蛋下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":32,"end":36,"text":"蛋壳变薄","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 成年鸡一般为轻度感染，严重感染的表现为下痢、日渐消瘦、产蛋下降、蛋壳变薄。

label: [{"start":11,"end":14,"text":"驱虫药","labels":["drug"]},{"start":5,"end":9,"text":"驱虫诊断","labels":["control"]},{"start":16,"end":20,"text":"驱虫诊断","labels":["control"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"蛔虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":34,"end":36,"text":"蛔虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":24,"end":25,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":52,"end":54,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":56,"end":59,"text":"驱蛔灵","labels":["drug"]},{"start":60,"end":63,"text":"驱虫净","labels":["drug"]},{"start":64,"end":67,"text":"四咪唑","labels":["drug"]},{"start":71,"end":74,"text":"驱蛔灵","labels":["drug"]},{"start":68,"end":70,"text":"饲服","labels":["control"]}]
text: 诊断方法：驱虫诊断。用驱虫药进行驱虫诊断，如发现鸡排出蛔虫即可确诊有蛔虫；方法是选取数只生长不良、消瘦的雏鸡，用驱蛔灵或驱虫净（四咪唑）饲服，驱蛔灵的用量是每公斤体重200～300毫克。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"杀鸡诊断","labels":["control"]},{"start":1,"end":2,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":12,"end":13,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":30,"end":33,"text":"蛔虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"蛔虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"肠道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 杀鸡诊断：如有必要还可杀鸡检查肠道情况，发现蛔虫即可以诊断有蛔虫病。

label: [{"start":5,"end":18,"text":"做好鸡舍内外的清洁卫生工作","labels":["control"]},{"start":7,"end":8,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"鸡粪","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":44,"end":60,"text":"料槽等用具经常清洗并且用开水消毒","labels":["type"]},{"start":31,"end":43,"text":"小面积地面可以用开水处理","labels":["type"]}]
text: 预防方法：做好鸡舍内外的清洁卫生工作，经常清除鸡粪及残余饲料，小面积地面可以用开水处理。料槽等用具经常清洗并且用开水消毒。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"蛔虫卵","labels":["disease"]},{"start":29,"end":32,"text":"蛔虫卵","labels":["disease"]},{"start":55,"end":59,"text":"服药驱虫","labels":["control"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 蛔虫卵在50°C以上很快死亡，粪便经堆沤发酵可以杀死虫卵，蛔虫卵在阴湿地方可以生存6个月。鸡群每年进行1～2次服药驱虫。

label: [{"start":5,"end":9,"text":"中药治疗","labels":["control"]},{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"中药","labels":["drug"]},{"start":10,"end":14,"text":"竹叶花椒","labels":["drug"]},{"start":27,"end":28,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":35,"end":38,"text":"拌料喂","labels":["control"]}]
text: 治疗方法：中药治疗，竹叶花椒15克，文火炒黄研末，每只鸡每次0.02克拌料喂，每天2次，连喂3天。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"烟草","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 烟草切碎15克，文火炒焦研碎，按2%比例拌入饲料，每天2次，连喂3～7天。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"成药治疗","labels":["control"]},{"start":5,"end":11,"text":"左旋咪唑片剂","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 成药治疗：左旋咪唑片剂：每千克体重口服38-48毫克(有效成分)/日。
